('89924','30956','5','Modern villa with sea views in Santa Ponsa'),
('89925','30957','5','Nova Santa Ponsa is one of the popular residential areas in the southwest of Mallorca. The excellent infrastructure and short connections to various marinas, golf courses, supermarkets and internally schools, make this residential area so attractive to many villa owners.\r\nThe villa in a contemporary style is currently being built on a 1.537m ² large hillside plot with sea- and countryside views.\r\nThe 906m² constructed area is spread over 2 levels and underground parking with space for up to 6 cars.\r\nLarge panoramic windows give the villa a transparent and with light flooded ambience. All 4 bedrooms and a guest apartment have a chic bathroom en suite. The Simatic kitchen with Gaggenau leaves nothing to be desired. For fine facilities include , inter alia, windows from Schücco, BUSS home automation control, Phillipp Stark fittings, Minotti furniture etc. A sauna, a wine cellar, a gym and an outdoor swimming pool surrounded by a landscaped garden, complete the offer.\r\nCompletion of the villa will be summer 2016\r\n\r\n'),
